    slug: `caring-campus-highlighted`,
    title: `Lawson's Legacy of Caring Highlighted Nationally`,
    date: '2025-01-30',
    category: 'Community',
    excerpt: `Lawson State's designation as a Caring Campus recently featured on national site.`,
    image: `https://www.lawsonstate.edu/news/DSC_0399.JPG`,
