    slug: `spring-registration-2025-open`,
    title: `Register now for Spring 2025`,
    date: '2024-01-01',
    category: 'Academics',
    excerpt: `Spring registration is open for early 2025. Classes begin January 9.`,
    image: `https://www.lawsonstate.edu/news/20250104_160117265_iOS.jpg`,
    imageAlt: `registration volunteers`,
    body: [
      `Start the New Year with a Fresh Focus on Your Future---At Lawson State`,
      `It's official: 2025 is here, bringing the perfect opportunity to focus on your future. Whether you are a recent high school graduate, a working professional seeking new skills, or someone looking to finish what you started years ago, Lawson State Community College is ready to help you achieve your goals.`,
      `Now is the time to take that first step. Join us for the Spring 2025 Registration Drive-In on Saturday, January 4, from 9 a.m. to 2 p.m. at the Academic Success Center on the Lawson State Birmingham campus.`,
      `During the Spring Registration Drive-In, you will have access to:`,
      `* Academic program advising* Class registration* College admissions support* Financial aid assistance* Placement testing`,
      `New Year, New Goals`,
      `"At Lawson State, we believe in helping people reach their goals," said Dorian Waluyn, executive director for strategic initiatives and external affairs. "Our affordable tuition, flexible class schedules, and supportive environment set students of all ages and backgrounds up for success."`,
      `Whether you are a recent high school graduate taking the first step toward a degree, a working professional looking to advance or change careers, or an adult learner ready to earn your GED or credentials, Lawson State has programs and resources to fit your needs.`,
      `"No matter where you are in your journey, our advisors are here to guide you," Mr. Waluyn added. "From transferring credits to finding the perfect career or technical program, we will help you create a plan that works for your life and goals."`,
      `Contact Lawson State to get started`,
      `The hardest part is starting, but you don't have to do it alone. Make 2025 the year you invest in yourself and your future. Email admissions@lawsonstate.edu or text 205-707-6422 to learn more.`
    ],
